---
description: Safety and production rules for n8n work
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

When changing n8n workflows:

- separate draft/editor success from published/production success
- identify credentials and side effects before editing
- validate node configs before workflow-level validation
- call out loop, merge, dedupe, and item-linking risks explicitly
- for AI workflows, require at least one evaluation path and one fallback path
- for release work, mention source control, environment promotion, and rollback posture

